&lt;h1&gt;ABOUT HAPPY MONEY&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Happy Money is a consumer finance company that empowers people to achieve their goals through simple, transparent loans funded by trusted financial institutions. Through its proprietary lending platform, Hive, Happy Money delivers a fully digital experience that simplifies borrowing for consumers and helps credit unions, banks and asset managers diversify balance sheets and scale with confidence.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Happy Money’s end-to-end loan origination and participation programs provide partners with turnkey access to high-performing assets, underpinned by disciplined credit expertise and robust risk management. Together with its lending partners, Happy Money has originated more than $6.5 billion in loans to help over 350,000 people take greater control of their financial futures. Learn more at happymoney.com.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;GENERAL APPLICATION&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Thank you for your interest in Happy Money!&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;This General Application of Interest allows our team to thoughtfully collect the resumes of talented candidates who reach out to us wanting to work for Happy Money. When we have an active job posting, our Talent team will also review the resumes submitted to this General Application.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;u&gt;What to expect when submitting a General Application:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;We will keep your resume on file.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;We will regularly review your resume based on active job posting criteria.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;We will reach out to you if your experience fits the requirements of an active role.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;u&gt;What NOT to expect when submitting a General Application:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;An immediate interview with our team.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Regularly updates from us on the status of active roles (so keep an eye on our Careers page!)&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;We&#39;re honored that you&#39;re interested in joining our Happy Money&#39;s mission of helping people achieve their goals through responsible lending. We&#39;ll be in touch if there&#39;s a good match with your experience and one of your future roles!&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;BENEFITS &amp;amp; PERKS&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generous medical, dental, and vision insurance options&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;401k Plan with a matching contribution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible PTO&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monthly Health and Wellness Days&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;12 Weeks Paid Parental Leave&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Company-paid short &amp;amp; long term disability and life insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monthly tech stipend to help cover expenses for remote work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Happy Money is a 100% fully distributed workforce&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h1&gt;ABOUT HAPPY MONEY&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Happy Money is a consumer finance company that empowers people to achieve their goals through simple, transparent loans funded by trusted financial institutions. Through its proprietary lending platform, Hive, Happy Money delivers a fully digital experience that simplifies borrowing for consumers and helps credit unions, banks and asset managers diversify balance sheets and scale with confidence. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Happy Money’s end-to-end loan origination and participation programs provide partners with turnkey access to high-performing assets, underpinned by disciplined credit expertise and robust risk management. Together with its lending partners, Happy Money has originated more than $6.5 billion in loans to help nearly 350,000 people take greater control of their financial futures. Learn more at happymoney.com. View our &lt;a href=&quot;https://drive.google.com/file/d/1PlDoDVlGPfcmkNK5meAmsnFV6DVuiypG/view?usp=sharing&quot;&gt;Employee Privacy Policy&lt;/a&gt; here.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Happy Money is a 100% fully distributed company. Remote work doesn’t mean less work, we work full-time jobs and show up to them fully every day. To learn more about our values and the way we work, review our &lt;a href=&quot;https://drive.google.com/file/d/1wtjH-1Y9UDgAGX_5AjcSvF3y08zf3t1M/view?usp=sharing&quot;&gt;Happy Money Way Overview!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;ABOUT THE ROLE&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Happy Money seeks a strategic Head of Acquisition Marketing to own and scale our customer acquisition capabilities, with a primary focus on driving profitable loan originations. This is a builder&#39;s role for a data-driven leader who can set strategy and has a proven track record building a coordinated, multi-channel acquisition engine and scaling it efficiently. You will strike the balance between aggressive growth and disciplined spend to deliver optimized customer acquisition costs, and you&#39;ll anticipate where the market, competition, and channels are heading and position Happy Money ahead of them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will lead a high-impact team responsible for executing and optimizing multi-channel campaigns (direct mail, digital, lead generation, and affiliate partnerships) using data, experimentation, and rigorous analysis to drive growth while achieving profitability targets. The role owns both performance marketing and brand, with near-term focus and resource intensity weighted toward customer acquisition. Brand evolution will be sequenced as loan growth scales and investment capacity expands.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role partners closely with the Head of Lifecycle Marketing, who owns the existing-borrower and lead-management side of the business. The partnership between Acquisition and Lifecycle is at the core of Happy Money&#39;s marketing function: together these roles drive substantial demand for Happy Money&#39;s products while maximizing the lifetime value of our customers and the monetization of acquired leads. At Happy Money we expect leaders to be a player-coach. This role will need to set strategy and roll up your sleeves to execute.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You thrive in a fast-paced environment, lead and mentor strong teams, and collaborate seamlessly with leaders across Credit/Risk &amp;amp; Analytics, Finance, Technology, and Operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
